sections.heading: to kill deer, antelope, or elk; tagging and storage
sections.text: The commission shall provide by regulations for the tagging and storage of the carcasses of deer, antelope, or elk after the close of any such limited season in accordance with section 37-508.SourceLaws 1945, c. 85, ยง 2, p. 305;Laws 1953, c. 124, ยง
